RunReportRequest.Rd

RunReportRequest Object

RunReportRequest(
  entity = NULL,
  metrics = NULL,
  currencyCode = NULL,
  orderBys = NULL,
  metricFilter = NULL,
  cohortSpec = NULL,
  metricAggregations = NULL,
  dimensions = NULL,
  dateRanges = NULL,
  keepEmptyRows = NULL,
  dimensionFilter = NULL,
  limit = NULL,
  offset = NULL,
  returnPropertyQuota = NULL
)

Arguments

entity

A property whose events are tracked
metrics

The metrics requested and displayed
currencyCode

A currency code in ISO4217 format, such as 'AED', 'USD', 'JPY'
orderBys

Specifies how rows are ordered in the response - see ga_data_order
metricFilter

The filter clause of metrics - see ga_data_filter
cohortSpec

Cohort group associated with this request
metricAggregations

Aggregation of metrics. Aggregated metric values will be shown in rows where the dimensionValues are set to "RESERVED_(MetricAggregation)".
dimensions

The dimensions requested and displayed
dateRanges

Date ranges of data to read, can send up to 4 date ranges (a vector of 8 dates spanning 1 year)
keepEmptyRows

If false, rows with metrics being 0 will not be returned
dimensionFilter

The filter clause of dimensions - see ga_data_filter
limit

The number of rows to return - use -1 to return all rows
offset

The row count of the start row
returnPropertyQuota

Toggles whether to return the current state of this Analytics Property's

Value

RunReportRequest object

Details

Autogenerated via gar_create_api_objects The request to generate a report.
